{
  "video_id": "zMGE3mbS9NY",
  "title": "Alessandra Orofino: It’s our city. Let’s fix it",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13401.0,
      "end_time": 16955.0,
      "text": "Fifty-four percent of the world&#39;s population"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16955.0,
      "end_time": 19535.0,
      "text": "lives in our cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19536.0,
      "end_time": 21181.0,
      "text": "In developing countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21181.0,
      "end_time": 23461.0,
      "text": "one third of that population"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 23461.0,
      "end_time": 26407.0,
      "text": "is living in slums."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 26408.0,
      "end_time": 31400.0,
      "text": "Seventy-five percent of global energy consumption"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31400.0,
      "end_time": 34890.0,
      "text": "occurs in our cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34900.0,
      "end_time": 36599.0,
      "text": "and 80 percent of gas emissions"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36599.0,
      "end_time": 38354.0,
      "text": "that cause global warming"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38354.0,
      "end_time": 41391.0,
      "text": "come from our cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41392.0,
      "end_time": 44417.0,
      "text": "So things that you and I might think about"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 44417.0,
      "end_time": 46532.0,
      "text": "as global problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 46532.0,
      "end_time": 49180.0,
      "text": "like climate change, the energy crisis"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49180.0,
      "end_time": 50842.0,
      "text": "or poverty,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50842.0,
      "end_time": 55702.0,
      "text": "are really, in many ways, city problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55702.0,
      "end_time": 57564.0,
      "text": "They will not be solved"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 57564.0,
      "end_time": 60582.0,
      "text": "unless people who live in cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60582.0,
      "end_time": 62501.0,
      "text": "like most of us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 62501.0,
      "end_time": 65292.0,
      "text": "actually start doing a better job,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65293.00000000001,
      "end_time": 69249.0,
      "text": "because right now, we are  not doing a very good one."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 69249.0,
      "end_time": 72585.0,
      "text": "And that becomes very clear"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72585.0,
      "end_time": 76479.0,
      "text": "when we look into three aspects of city life:"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76479.0,
      "end_time": 80605.0,
      "text": "first, our citizens&#39; willingness to engage"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80605.0,
      "end_time": 83417.0,
      "text": "with democratic institutions;"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83417.0,
      "end_time": 88221.0,
      "text": "second, our cities&#39; ability to really include"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 88221.0,
      "end_time": 90763.0,
      "text": "all of their residents;"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 90763.0,
      "end_time": 93940.0,
      "text": "and lastly, our own ability"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 93940.0,
      "end_time": 98405.0,
      "text": "to live fulfilling and happy lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 98405.0,
      "end_time": 100184.0,
      "text": "When it comes to engagement,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 100184.0,
      "end_time": 103114.0,
      "text": "the data is very clear."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 103114.0,
      "end_time": 105195.0,
      "text": "Voter turnout around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 105195.0,
      "end_time": 107636.0,
      "text": "peaked in the late &#39;80s,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 107636.0,
      "end_time": 109481.0,
      "text": "and it has been declining at a pace"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 109481.0,
      "end_time": 112542.0,
      "text": "that we have never seen before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 112543.0,
      "end_time": 116138.0,
      "text": "and if those numbers are bad at the national level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 116138.0,
      "end_time": 118147.0,
      "text": "at the level of our cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 118147.0,
      "end_time": 121236.0,
      "text": "they are just dismal."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 121236.0,
      "end_time": 122830.0,
      "text": "In the last two years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 122830.0,
      "end_time": 125331.0,
      "text": "two of the world&#39;s most consolidated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 125331.0,
      "end_time": 129166.0,
      "text": "oldest democracies, the U.S. and France,"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 129166.0,
      "end_time": 132971.0,
      "text": "held nationwide municipal elections."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 132971.0,
      "end_time": 136871.0,
      "text": "In France, voter turnout hit a record low."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 136871.0,
      "end_time": 140933.0,
      "text": "Almost 40 percent of voters decided"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 140933.0,
      "end_time": 143620.0,
      "text": "not to show up."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 143621.0,
      "end_time": 146710.0,
      "text": "In the U.S., the numbers were even scarier."
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 146710.0,
      "end_time": 148987.0,
      "text": "In some American cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 148987.0,
      "end_time": 153981.0,
      "text": "voter turnout was close to five percent."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 153981.0,
      "end_time": 155769.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ll let that sink in for a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 155770.0,
      "end_time": 158188.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re talking about democratic cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 158188.0,
      "end_time": 161563.0,
      "text": "in which 95 percent of people"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 161563.0,
      "end_time": 163981.0,
      "text": "decided that it was not important"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 163981.0,
      "end_time": 166726.0,
      "text": "to elect their leaders."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 166726.0,
      "end_time": 170380.0,
      "text": "The city of L.A., a city of four million people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 170380.0,
      "end_time": 175309.0,
      "text": "elected its mayor with just a bit over 200,000 votes."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 175309.0,
      "end_time": 177795.0,
      "text": "That was the lowest turnout the city had seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 177795.0,
      "end_time": 180676.0,
      "text": "in 100 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 180676.0,
      "end_time": 183720.0,
      "text": "Right here, in my city of Rio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 183720.0,
      "end_time": 186794.0,
      "text": "in spite of mandatory voting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 186794.0,
      "end_time": 190292.0,
      "text": "almost 30 percent of the voting population"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 190292.0,
      "end_time": 192857.0,
      "text": "chose to either annul their votes"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 192857.0,
      "end_time": 195489.0,
      "text": "or stay home and pay a fine"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 195489.0,
      "end_time": 198820.0,
      "text": "in the last mayoral elections."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 198820.0,
      "end_time": 201138.0,
      "text": "When it comes to inclusiveness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 201139.0,
      "end_time": 204244.0,
      "text": "our cities are not the best cases of success either,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 204244.0,
      "end_time": 207134.0,
      "text": "and again, you don&#39;t need to look very far"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 207134.0,
      "end_time": 208888.0,
      "text": "in order to find proof of that."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 208889.0,
      "end_time": 213388.0,
      "text": "The city of Rio is incredibly unequal."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 213388.0,
      "end_time": 215357.0,
      "text": "This is Leblon."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 215357.0,
      "end_time": 218461.0,
      "text": "Leblon is the city&#39;s richest neighborhood."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 218461.0,
      "end_time": 220900.0,
      "text": "And this is Complexo do Alemão."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 220900.0,
      "end_time": 223164.0,
      "text": "This is where over 70,000"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 223164.0,
      "end_time": 226415.0,
      "text": "of the city&#39;s poorest residents live."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 226415.0,
      "end_time": 230100.0,
      "text": "Leblon has an HDI, a Human Development Index,"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 230100.0,
      "end_time": 233390.0,
      "text": "of .967."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 233390.0,
      "end_time": 237210.0,
      "text": "That is higher than Norway, Switzerland"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 237211.0,
      "end_time": 239452.0,
      "text": "or Sweden."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 239452.0,
      "end_time": 243181.0,
      "text": "Complexo do Alemão has an HDI of .711."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 243181.0,
      "end_time": 246111.0,
      "text": "It sits somewhere in between the HDI"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 246111.0,
      "end_time": 249328.0,
      "text": "of Algeria and Gabon."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 249328.0,
      "end_time": 254109.0,
      "text": "So Rio, like so many cities across the global South,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 254109.0,
      "end_time": 257790.0,
      "text": "is a place where you can go from northern Europe"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 257790.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258979.00000000003,
      "text": "to sub-Saharan Africa"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 258980.00000000003,
      "end_time": 261984.00000000003,
      "text": "in the space of 30 minutes."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 261983.0,
      "end_time": 263693.0,
      "text": "If you drive, that is."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 263693.0,
      "end_time": 268440.0,
      "text": "If you take public transit, it&#39;s about two hours."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 268440.0,
      "end_time": 272299.0,
      "text": "And lastly, perhaps most importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 272299.0,
      "end_time": 274780.0,
      "text": "cities, with the incredible wealth"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 274780.0,
      "end_time": 277282.0,
      "text": "of relations that they enable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 277282.0,
      "end_time": 281159.0,
      "text": "could be the ideal places for human happiness"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 281160.0,
      "end_time": 282562.0,
      "text": "to flourish."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 282562.0,
      "end_time": 284987.0,
      "text": "We like being around people."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 284987.0,
      "end_time": 287383.0,
      "text": "We are social animals."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 287383.0,
      "end_time": 290600.0,
      "text": "Instead, countries where urbanization"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 290600.0,
      "end_time": 294227.0,
      "text": "has already peaked seem to be the very countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 294228.0,
      "end_time": 298880.0,
      "text": "in which cities have stopped making us happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 298880.0,
      "end_time": 301484.0,
      "text": "The United States population has suffered"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 301484.0,
      "end_time": 304464.0,
      "text": "from a general decrease in happiness"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 304464.0,
      "end_time": 307666.0,
      "text": "for the past three decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 307666.0,
      "end_time": 310640.0,
      "text": "and the main reason is this."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 310640.0,
      "end_time": 313542.0,
      "text": "The American way of building cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 313542.0,
      "end_time": 316253.0,
      "text": "has caused good quality public spaces"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 316253.0,
      "end_time": 318236.0,
      "text": "to virtually disappear in many,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 318237.0,
      "end_time": 319992.0,
      "text": "many American cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 319992.0,
      "end_time": 321989.0,
      "text": "and as a result, they have seen"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 321989.0,
      "end_time": 324544.0,
      "text": "a decline of relations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 324544.0,
      "end_time": 326748.0,
      "text": "of the things that make us happy."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 326748.0,
      "end_time": 328795.0,
      "text": "Many studies show an increase"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 328795.0,
      "end_time": 333486.0,
      "text": "in solitude and a decrease in solidarity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 333486.0,
      "end_time": 338142.0,
      "text": "honesty, and social and civic participation."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 338142.0,
      "end_time": 341506.0,
      "text": "So how do we start building cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 341506.0,
      "end_time": 344116.0,
      "text": "that make us care?"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 344116.0,
      "end_time": 348750.0,
      "text": "Cities that value their most important asset:"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 348750.0,
      "end_time": 351349.0,
      "text": "the incredible diversity"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 351349.0,
      "end_time": 353555.0,
      "text": "of the people who live in them?"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 353555.0,
      "end_time": 357212.0,
      "text": "Cities that make us happy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 357212.0,
      "end_time": 359719.0,
      "text": "Well, I believe that if we want to change"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 359719.0,
      "end_time": 362271.0,
      "text": "what our cities look like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 362271.0,
      "end_time": 364961.0,
      "text": "then we really have to change"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 364961.0,
      "end_time": 367504.0,
      "text": "the decision-making processes"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 367504.0,
      "end_time": 371328.0,
      "text": "that have given us the results  that we have right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 371328.0,
      "end_time": 374500.0,
      "text": "We need a participation revolution,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 374500.0,
      "end_time": 377374.0,
      "text": "and we need it fast."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 377374.0,
      "end_time": 382712.0,
      "text": "The idea of voting as our  only exercise in citizenship"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 382712.0,
      "end_time": 385670.0,
      "text": "does not make sense anymore."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 385670.0,
      "end_time": 388199.0,
      "text": "People are tired of only being treated"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 388199.0,
      "end_time": 392372.0,
      "text": "as empowered individuals every few years"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 392372.0,
      "end_time": 395522.0,
      "text": "when it&#39;s time to delegate that power"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 395522.0,
      "end_time": 397897.0,
      "text": "to someone else."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 397897.0,
      "end_time": 400842.0,
      "text": "If the protests that swept Brazil"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 400842.0,
      "end_time": 405813.0,
      "text": "in June 2013 have taught us anything,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 405814.0,
      "end_time": 408649.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s that every time we try"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 408649.0,
      "end_time": 411101.0,
      "text": "to exercise our power"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 411101.0,
      "end_time": 413958.0,
      "text": "outside of an electoral context,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 413958.0,
      "end_time": 419212.0,
      "text": "we are beaten up, humiliated or arrested."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 419212.0,
      "end_time": 422419.0,
      "text": "And this needs to change,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 422419.0,
      "end_time": 424633.0,
      "text": "because when it does,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 424633.0,
      "end_time": 426894.0,
      "text": "not only will people re-engage"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 426894.0,
      "end_time": 429380.0,
      "text": "with the structures of representation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 429380.0,
      "end_time": 432654.0,
      "text": "but also complement these structures"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 432654.0,
      "end_time": 439572.0,
      "text": "with direct, effective, and  collective decision making,"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 439572.0,
      "end_time": 441496.0,
      "text": "decision making of the kind"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 441496.0,
      "end_time": 443542.0,
      "text": "that attacks inequality"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 443542.0,
      "end_time": 446782.0,
      "text": "by its very inclusive nature,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 446782.0,
      "end_time": 448604.0,
      "text": "decision making of the kind"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 448605.0,
      "end_time": 450821.0,
      "text": "that can change our cities"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 450821.0,
      "end_time": 453937.0,
      "text": "into better places for us to live."
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 453937.0,
      "end_time": 457416.0,
      "text": "But there is a catch, obviously:"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 457416.0,
      "end_time": 460157.0,
      "text": "Enabling widespread participation"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 460157.0,
      "end_time": 462115.0,
      "text": "and redistributing power"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 462115.0,
      "end_time": 464840.0,
      "text": "can be a logistical nightmare,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 464840.0,
      "end_time": 467128.0,
      "text": "and there&#39;s where technology can play"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 467129.0,
      "end_time": 469306.0,
      "text": "an incredibly helpful role,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 469306.0,
      "end_time": 472388.0,
      "text": "by making it easier for people to organize,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 472388.0,
      "end_time": 474452.0,
      "text": "communicate and make decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 474452.0,
      "end_time": 476690.0,
      "text": "without having to be in the same room"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 476690.0,
      "end_time": 478952.0,
      "text": "at the same time."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 478952.0,
      "end_time": 480853.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately for us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 480853.0,
      "end_time": 483879.0,
      "text": "when it comes to fostering democratic processes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 483879.0,
      "end_time": 486964.0,
      "text": "our city governments have not used technology"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 486964.0,
      "end_time": 489942.0,
      "text": "to its full potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 489942.0,
      "end_time": 493159.0,
      "text": "So far, most city governments have been effective"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 493159.0,
      "end_time": 497742.0,
      "text": "at using tech to turn citizens into human sensors"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 497742.0,
      "end_time": 501450.0,
      "text": "who serve authorities with data on the city:"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 501450.0,
      "end_time": 505456.0,
      "text": "potholes, fallen trees or broken lamps."
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 505456.0,
      "end_time": 507886.0,
      "text": "They have also, to a lesser extent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 507886.0,
      "end_time": 511486.0,
      "text": "invited people to participate in improving"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 511486.0,
      "end_time": 513100.0,
      "text": "the outcome of decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 513100.0,
      "end_time": 516412.0,
      "text": "that were already made for them,"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 516412.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517987.00000000006,
      "text": "just like my mom when I was eight"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 517986.0,
      "end_time": 519752.0,
      "text": "and she told me that I had a choice:"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 519753.00000000006,
      "end_time": 521330.00000000006,
      "text": "I had to be in bed by 8 p.m.,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 521330.00000000006,
      "end_time": 525243.0,
      "text": "but I could choose my pink pajamas or my blue pajamas."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 525243.0,
      "end_time": 527482.0,
      "text": "That&#39;s not participation,"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 527482.0,
      "end_time": 531227.0,
      "text": "and in fact, governments have not been very good"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 531227.0,
      "end_time": 534130.0,
      "text": "at using technology to enable participation"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 534130.0,
      "end_time": 536800.0,
      "text": "on what matters —"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 536800.0,
      "end_time": 538393.0,
      "text": "the way we allocate our budget,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 538393.0,
      "end_time": 540615.0,
      "text": "the way we occupy our land,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 540615.0,
      "end_time": 544164.0,
      "text": "and the way we manage our natural resources."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 544164.0,
      "end_time": 546278.0,
      "text": "Those are the kinds of decisions"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 546278.0,
      "end_time": 549158.0,
      "text": "that can actually impact global problems"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 549158.0,
      "end_time": 552980.0,
      "text": "that manifest themselves in our cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 552980.0,
      "end_time": 554506.0,
      "text": "The good news is,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 554506.0,
      "end_time": 556369.0,
      "text": "and I do have good news to share with you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 556369.0,
      "end_time": 560666.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t need to wait for governments to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 560666.0,
      "end_time": 562636.0,
      "text": "I have reason to believe"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 562636.0,
      "end_time": 565223.0,
      "text": "that it&#39;s possible for citizens to build"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 565224.0,
      "end_time": 569757.0,
      "text": "their own structures of participation."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 569757.0,
      "end_time": 572558.0,
      "text": "Three years ago, I cofounded an organization"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 572558.0,
      "end_time": 575450.0,
      "text": "called Meu Rio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 575450.0,
      "end_time": 578125.0,
      "text": "and we make it easier for people in the city of Rio"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 578125.0,
      "end_time": 581704.0,
      "text": "to organize around causes and places"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 581704.0,
      "end_time": 584300.0,
      "text": "that they care about in their own city,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 584301.0,
      "end_time": 586990.0,
      "text": "and have an impact on those causes and places"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 586990.0,
      "end_time": 589318.0,
      "text": "every day."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 589318.0,
      "end_time": 592600.0,
      "text": "In these past three years, Meu Rio grew"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 592600.0,
      "end_time": 597928.0,
      "text": "to a network of 160,000 citizens of Rio."
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 597928.0,
      "end_time": 601833.0,
      "text": "About 40 percent of those  members are young people"
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 601833.0,
      "end_time": 604720.0,
      "text": "aged 20 to 29."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 604720.0,
      "end_time": 608996.0,
      "text": "That is one in every 15 young people"
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 608996.0,
      "end_time": 612828.0,
      "text": "of that age in Rio today."
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 612828.0,
      "end_time": 616459.0,
      "text": "Amongst our members is this adorable little girl,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 616460.0,
      "end_time": 618509.0,
      "text": "Bia, to your right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 618509.0,
      "end_time": 621636.0,
      "text": "and Bia was just 11 years old"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 621636.0,
      "end_time": 624572.0,
      "text": "when she started a campaign using one of our tools"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 624572.0,
      "end_time": 628161.0,
      "text": "to save her model public school from demolition."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 628161.0,
      "end_time": 630252.0,
      "text": "Her school actually ranks among the best"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 630253.0,
      "end_time": 632525.0,
      "text": "public schools in the country,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 632525.0,
      "end_time": 634257.0,
      "text": "and it was going to be demolished"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 634257.0,
      "end_time": 636810.0,
      "text": "by the Rio de Janeiro state government"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 636811.0,
      "end_time": 638701.0,
      "text": "to build, I kid you not,"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 638701.0,
      "end_time": 641524.0,
      "text": "a parking lot for the World Cup"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 641524.0,
      "end_time": 643870.0,
      "text": "right before the event happened."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 643870.0,
      "end_time": 646364.0,
      "text": "Bia started a campaign, and we even watched"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 646364.0,
      "end_time": 649747.0,
      "text": "her school 24/7 through webcam monitoring,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 649747.0,
      "end_time": 651761.0,
      "text": "and many months afterwards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 651761.0,
      "end_time": 653391.0,
      "text": "the government changed their minds."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 653392.0,
      "end_time": 656316.0,
      "text": "Bia&#39;s school stayed in place."
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 656316.0,
      "end_time": 658487.0,
      "text": "There&#39;s also Jovita."
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 658487.0,
      "end_time": 660759.0,
      "text": "She&#39;s an amazing woman whose daughter"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 660759.0,
      "end_time": 663420.0,
      "text": "went missing about 10 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 663420.0,
      "end_time": 665854.0,
      "text": "and since then, she has been looking"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 665855.0,
      "end_time": 667390.0,
      "text": "for her daughter."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 667390.0,
      "end_time": 669814.0,
      "text": "In that process, she found out"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 669815.0,
      "end_time": 672368.0,
      "text": "that first, she was not alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 672368.0,
      "end_time": 674956.0,
      "text": "In the last year alone, 2013,"
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 674956.0,
      "end_time": 676830.0,
      "text": "6,000 people disappeared"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 676830.0,
      "end_time": 678706.0,
      "text": "in the state of Rio."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 678706.0,
      "end_time": 681334.0,
      "text": "But she also found out that in spite of that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 681334.0,
      "end_time": 685285.0,
      "text": "Rio had no centralized intelligence system"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 685285.0,
      "end_time": 688589.0,
      "text": "for solving missing persons cases."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 688590.0,
      "end_time": 691160.0,
      "text": "In other Brazilian cities, those systems"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 691160.0,
      "end_time": 693550.0,
      "text": "have helped solve up to 80 percent"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 693550.0,
      "end_time": 695585.0,
      "text": "of missing persons cases."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 695586.0,
      "end_time": 697329.0,
      "text": "She started a campaign,"
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 697329.0,
      "end_time": 701310.0,
      "text": "and after the secretary of  security got 16,000 emails"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 701311.0,
      "end_time": 704124.0,
      "text": "from people asking him to do this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 704124.0,
      "end_time": 707106.0,
      "text": "he responded, and started to build a police unit"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 707106.0,
      "end_time": 708930.0,
      "text": "specializing in those cases."
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 708930.0,
      "end_time": 712286.0,
      "text": "It was open to the public at the end of last month,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 712286.0,
      "end_time": 714137.0,
      "text": "and Jovita was there"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 714137.0,
      "end_time": 717161.0,
      "text": "giving interviews and being very fancy."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 717161.0,
      "end_time": 719000.0,
      "text": "And then, there is Leandro."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 719000.0,
      "end_time": 720723.0,
      "text": "Leandro is an amazing guy"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 720723.0,
      "end_time": 722639.0,
      "text": "in a slum in Rio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 722639.0,
      "end_time": 726620.0,
      "text": "and he created a recycling project in the slum."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 726620.0,
      "end_time": 728512.0,
      "text": "At the end of last year, December 16,"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 728512.0,
      "end_time": 730603.0,
      "text": "he received an eviction order"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 730604.0,
      "end_time": 732584.0,
      "text": "by the Rio de Janeiro state government"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 732584.0,
      "end_time": 736503.0,
      "text": "giving him two weeks to leave the space"
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 736504.0,
      "end_time": 740244.0,
      "text": "that he had been using for two years."
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 740244.0,
      "end_time": 742809.0,
      "text": "The plan was to hand it over to a developer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 742809.0,
      "end_time": 746228.0,
      "text": "who planned to turn it into a construction site."
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 746229.0,
      "end_time": 749297.0,
      "text": "Leandro started a campaign using one of our tools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 749297.0,
      "end_time": 750875.0,
      "text": "the Pressure Cooker,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 750875.0,
      "end_time": 753214.0,
      "text": "the same one that Bia and Jovita used,"
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 753214.0,
      "end_time": 756270.0,
      "text": "and the state government changed their minds"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 756270.0,
      "end_time": 759536.0,
      "text": "before Christmas Eve."
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 759536.0,
      "end_time": 762608.0,
      "text": "These stories make me happy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 762608.0,
      "end_time": 765655.0,
      "text": "but not just because they have happy endings."
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 765655.0,
      "end_time": 768401.0,
      "text": "They make me happy because they are"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 768401.0,
      "end_time": 771990.0,
      "text": "happy beginnings."
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 771100.0,
      "end_time": 773519.0,
      "text": "The teacher and parent community at Bia&#39;s school"
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 773519.0,
      "end_time": 775475.0,
      "text": "is looking for other ways they could improve"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 775475.0,
      "end_time": 778952.0,
      "text": "that space even further."
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 778952.0,
      "end_time": 780663.0,
      "text": "Leandro has ambitious plans"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 780663.0,
      "end_time": 783616.0,
      "text": "to take his model to other low-income communities in Rio,"
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 783616.0,
      "end_time": 786827.0,
      "text": "and Jovita is volunteering at the police unit"
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 786827.0,
      "end_time": 789667.0,
      "text": "that she helped created."
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 789667.0,
      "end_time": 792415.0,
      "text": "Bia, Jovita and Leandro"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 792415.0,
      "end_time": 794474.0,
      "text": "are living examples of something"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 794475.0,
      "end_time": 798570.0,
      "text": "that citizens and city  governments around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 798570.0,
      "end_time": 800461.0,
      "text": "need to know:"
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 800461.0,
      "end_time": 803788.0,
      "text": "We are ready."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 803788.0,
      "end_time": 806716.0,
      "text": "As citizens, we are ready"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 806716.0,
      "end_time": 810271.0,
      "text": "to decide on our common destinies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 810271.0,
      "end_time": 814290.0,
      "text": "because we know that the way we distribute power"
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 814290.0,
      "end_time": 819130.0,
      "text": "says a lot about how we actually value everyone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 819130.0,
      "end_time": 821360.0,
      "text": "and because we know"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 821360.0,
      "end_time": 824855.0,
      "text": "that enabling and participating in local politics"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 824855.0,
      "end_time": 826978.0,
      "text": "is a sign that we truly care"
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 826978.0,
      "end_time": 829168.0,
      "text": "about our relations to one another,"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 829168.0,
      "end_time": 830890.0,
      "text": "and we are ready to do this"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 830890.0,
      "end_time": 834907.0,
      "text": "in cities around the world right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 834907.0,
      "end_time": 837303.0,
      "text": "With the Our Cities network,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 837303.0,
      "end_time": 838640.0,
      "text": "the Meu Rio team"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 838640.0,
      "end_time": 840665.0,
      "text": "hopes to share what we have learned"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 840666.0,
      "end_time": 842622.0,
      "text": "with other people who want to create"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 842622.0,
      "end_time": 845883.0,
      "text": "similar initiatives in their own cities."
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 845884.0,
      "end_time": 848441.0,
      "text": "We have already started doing it in São Paulo"
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 848441.0,
      "end_time": 850137.0,
      "text": "with incredible results,"
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 850137.0,
      "end_time": 853444.0,
      "text": "and want to take it to cities around the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 853444.0,
      "end_time": 856368.0,
      "text": "through a network of citizen-centric,"
    },
    {
      "index": 294,
      "start_time": 856369.0,
      "end_time": 858746.0,
      "text": "citizen-led organizations"
    },
    {
      "index": 295,
      "start_time": 858746.0,
      "end_time": 860932.0,
      "text": "that can inspire us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 296,
      "start_time": 860932.0,
      "end_time": 864396.0,
      "text": "challenge us, and remind us to demand"
    },
    {
      "index": 297,
      "start_time": 864396.0,
      "end_time": 869447.0,
      "text": "real participation in our city lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 298,
      "start_time": 869447.0,
      "end_time": 871409.0,
      "text": "It is up to us"
    },
    {
      "index": 299,
      "start_time": 871409.0,
      "end_time": 873894.0,
      "text": "to decide whether we want schools"
    },
    {
      "index": 300,
      "start_time": 873894.0,
      "end_time": 876180.0,
      "text": "or parking lots,"
    },
    {
      "index": 301,
      "start_time": 876180.0,
      "end_time": 878512.0,
      "text": "community-driven recycling projects"
    },
    {
      "index": 302,
      "start_time": 878513.0,
      "end_time": 881116.0,
      "text": "or construction sites,"
    },
    {
      "index": 303,
      "start_time": 881116.0,
      "end_time": 883536.0,
      "text": "loneliness or solidarity, cars or buses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 304,
      "start_time": 883536.0,
      "end_time": 887234.0,
      "text": "and it is our responsibility to do that now,"
    },
    {
      "index": 305,
      "start_time": 887235.0,
      "end_time": 890659.0,
      "text": "for ourselves, for our families,"
    },
    {
      "index": 306,
      "start_time": 890659.0,
      "end_time": 894753.0,
      "text": "for the people who make our lives worth living,"
    },
    {
      "index": 307,
      "start_time": 894753.0,
      "end_time": 897620.0,
      "text": "and for the incredible creativity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 308,
      "start_time": 897620.0,
      "end_time": 901270.0,
      "text": "beauty, and wonder that make our cities,"
    },
    {
      "index": 309,
      "start_time": 901270.0,
      "end_time": 903614.0,
      "text": "in spite of all of their problems,"
    },
    {
      "index": 310,
      "start_time": 903614.0,
      "end_time": 907330.0,
      "text": "the greatest invention of our time."
    },
    {
      "index": 311,
      "start_time": 907330.0,
      "end_time": 909810.0,
      "text": "Obrigado. Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 312,
      "start_time": 909810.0,
      "end_time": 913800.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}